Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smpp.SmppObject

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BindResponse, CancelSMResp, DataSMResp, DeliverSMResp, EnquireLinkResp, GenericNack, QuerySMResp, ReplaceSMResp, SubmitMultiSMResp, SubmitSMResp, UnbindResp

    public abstract class Response
extends PDU
    Represents a PDU response. All classes which are used as SMPP response are derived from this class.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.1 $
    Author:
    Logica Mobile Networks SMPP Open Source Team
